            <h3>Social and Community Impact</h3>
            <p>Phase 2 aims to catalyze global change by expanding into high school-aged young adults, global Christian demographics, and online income seekers:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Empowering Young Adults:</strong> High school and college students gain tools for leadership, generosity, and community building.</li>
                <li><strong>Community Growth:</strong> Funds allocated to restoration of families, poverty alleviation, and Spirit-filled mentorship programs.</li>
                <li><strong>Ripple Effect:</strong> Encourages a cycle of giving that builds sustainable communities globally.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h3>Economic Impact</h3>
            <p>The program not only advances Kingdom work but also provides affiliates with substantial income opportunities:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Affiliates can earn an average of <strong>$40,000 annually</strong> through the program.</li>
                <li>Generates over <strong>$137 million</strong> in direct affiliate payouts by the end of Phase 2.</li>
                <li>Boosts local economies through community-driven projects and reinvestment.</li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="section">
            <h3>Spiritual Impact</h3>
            <p>Guided by Holy Spirit generosity, the program embodies the principles of Acts 2:44-45:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Unites believers across demographics to foster a spirit of generosity and Kingdom-building.</li>
                <li>Restores faith in the power of giving, making generosity a central act of worship and testimony.</li>
